<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_426_r1l2">Marggraf <expan>Fridrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_426_r1l3">cʒu Brandemburgk etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_426_r1l4">Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . Vns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> <expan>han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> vorcheẏmer <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_426_r1l6">vvie 
<del rend="strikethrough">Er mitſampt </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_426_r1l5">Jm </ab></add> <expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan> habe vnd kauffmanſchaft / cʒu Öllſnıcʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_426_r1l7">dabey Er <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> geleÿte gehabt hab / aufgehalten ſeẏ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_426_r1l8">woꝛden / Als Er <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan></del> gnaden das ſelber auch wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_426_r1l9">ercʒelen wirdt / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan></del> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_426_r1l10"><expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> darynne ewr gnedige <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_426_r1l11">geruchet cʒubevveẏſen / damit Jm dieſelb ſein habe vnd </ab>
